name: No one is here (CivilianZero)
description:
Welcome to NO ONE IS HERE 

The objective is to traverse deeper into the caves and reclaim salvage. 

Move with WASD 

Fire Torpedos with Space 

Ping Sonar with 1 

Move over Salvage to pick it up 

Thanks for playing!
